node.text:
Here’s an impressive #YOUTHPOWERHACKS statistic for you. 100% of the participants from our South Africa Hack said that they would go on to take action as a direct result of the hackathon!

Every single one of our participants demonstrated their determination to make positive change in their communities, and Lorencia is no different. She is passionate about helping young people develop the skills needed to navigate the digital world so that they can access jobs and educational opportunities.

Check out this voice note to learn more about Lorencia and why she is taking part in the Youth Power Hacks.

#Goal4 #Goal8 #Goal10 @restlessdevelopment
